    desc: "General Const Lab Calibration — part of General Tech Services — holds full EIAC accreditation to ISO 17025 covering 15 calibration disciplines — delivering technically valid, traceable calibration certificates recognized by regulatory authorities, quality auditors, and international clients across the UAE and GCC.",
  },
  {
    title: "General Tech Services Since 1998",
    desc: "With 26 plus years as a trusted calibration laboratory UAE since 1998, General Tech Services brings unmatched institutional knowledge, client relationships, and technical expertise to every calibration and industrial supply engagement across the UAE. Our General Tech Services calibration laboratory Sharjah UAE has been the benchmark for ISO 17025 accredited calibration services UAE quality since the company's founding.",
  },
  {
    title: "Authorized Mitutoyo Distributor UAE",
    desc: "As the authorized Mitutoyo distributor UAE, authorized WIKA distributor UAE, and authorized Norbar distributor UAE partner — and as authorized distributor for over 90 global brands — General Tech Services supplies genuine products with full manufacturer warranty and manufacturer-certified calibration services.",
  },
  {
    title: "On-Site and In-Lab Calibration Services UAE",
    desc: "Our fleet of over 20 service vehicles provides on-site calibration services UAE across all seven Emirates — minimizing operational downtime while maintaining full ISO 17025 traceability and audit-ready documentation.",
  },
  {
    title: "Industrial Calibration Services UAE for Every Sector",
    desc: "From oil and gas and manufacturing to healthcare, utilities, construction, aerospace, food and beverage, and pharmaceuticals — General Tech Services delivers professional industrial calibration services UAE tailored to the compliance requirements of every industry sector across the UAE.",
  },
  {
    title: "Professional Calibration Services UAE",
    desc: "As the most professional calibration services UAE provider since 1998, General Tech Services delivers audit-ready ISO 17025 calibration certificates, documented measurement uncertainty reporting, and technically valid results that meet the compliance requirements of UAE regulatory authorities.",
  },
  {
