    desc: "Our calibration laboratory with widest accreditation scope UAE covers 15 disciplines — Biomedical, Dimensional, Electrical, Flow, Force, Gas Analyser and Detector, Humidity, Mass, NDT, pH and Other Instruments, Pressure, Sound, Temperature, Torque, and Volumetric.",
  },
